# AI-k8s-Platform

Self-healing K8s platform for AI training: DCGM metrics → Prometheus → Operator → cordon/taint → evict → Job reschedule + checkpoint resume.

## Layout

- `cmd/operator`, `cmd/exporter` — binaries
- `internal/healing` — cordon, taint, eviction
- `internal/prometheus` — metric / alert queries
- `deploy/manifests` — RBAC and workloads

## Healing sequence

1. Alert (e.g. GPU XID on a node)
2. Cordon + taint the node
3. Evict training pods on that node
4. Job controller reschedules; new pod mounts latest checkpoint

Prefer minimal diffs; match existing Go and K8s patterns. See `AGENTS.md` and `说明文档.txt`.
